{"tid":131753,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無記錯係一個警察爆7警嘅資料岀黎？","createTime":"2017-02-23T09:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T16:30:10.000Z","uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3eb2c913d8d3732f2b69f4830bb97799d268f3","tid":131753,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f337ccc94b57efb08ff7383af753e6d1e72d51b","tid":131753,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"施恒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾好似話佢不誠實使用電腦<br />\n話佢有 child porn"},{"pid":"1c68dcf669fa7ac473a1e72605813a2d0197be4c","tid":131753,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"好似比人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7be8e849e81b584d7395f006ca934ca610e0cb5","tid":131753,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施恒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾好似話佢不誠實使用電腦<br />\n話佢有 child porn</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161102/19820112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161102%2F19820112&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=dd41ab63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161102%2F19820112&h=cf52d248\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161102/19820112</a><br />\nsze sir好似係指證其他惡意挑釁市民嘅差佬<br />\n<br />\n本報訊】「無間道」督察於前年佔領運動時，拍下兩名同袍於警隊內部電話簿的資料，上載到針對反佔中人士facebook群組，他其後被揭發涉藏有兒童色情影像。案件昨在區域法院續審，庭上播放督察被捕後的錄影紀錄，督察承認與群組支持佔領立場相近，他於群組讀到同僚挑釁市民消息後，出於好奇和想核實消息故起底，坦言上載照片時沒想到後果。<br />\n<br />\n不清楚孌童片來源<br />\n<br />\n被告施恒（30歲）承認不誠實取用電腦罪，但否認管有兒童色情物品罪。施將同僚資料上載到「反佔中認人組」，他在會面中指該群組支持佔領運動，與其個人立場相近，加上他想知示威現場資訊，故訂閱群組。前年11月27日，群組有人指兩名警員挑釁市民，並註明警員編號。施稱網上有不少以訛傳訛、甚至具惡意的假消息，故用警隊內部網絡查證編號是否虛構，同時滿足好奇心。至於查證後為何上載相片，施解釋想幫群組的其他人核實消息。<br />\n警方在施的手提電腦和外置硬碟中搜出268段兒童色情片及3張同類相片，施在錄影會面中稱不清楚影片來源，他不是片中人或拍攝者。其間警員讀出影片檔案名稱，包含「best of the best fuxk」、「10 yo Russian girl」、「個人小生援助交際」等字眼。聆訊今續。<br />\n案件編號：DCCC204/15<br />\n■記者勞東來&nbsp;"},{"pid":"aa65c927383c36a7a27d87a9b143f61f768ca642","tid":131753,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"係七警其中一個上司<br />\n蘋果動有講<br />\n我搵搵先"},{"pid":"ed4d51f5e37b00d8ec50e7bd738ec2ece8ef5278","tid":131753,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"報料者應該好慘"},{"pid":"d894c91a022271e6206634eff765bc5444197884","tid":131753,"uid":65659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"好似話佢屋企部電腦有動畫，搞到加多條罪"},{"pid":"fd2c3cb2463b1ea5d348fd3331a6b4713bfd2c48","tid":131753,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"藍絲唔係支持黑警嚴正執法咩，明明係黑警落案拉 7 犯"},{"pid":"0307cef0ed8625ad54c84825cd78c3e9f2c3027b","tid":131753,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"施恆呢d正義之士先配稱為香港警察<br />\n佢單案搞成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03886772780bdc1c375c8a8d39aba2affd8aed6d","tid":131753,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施恒呢d正義之士先配稱為香港警察<br />\n佢單案搞成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b9ff9a362fa7ca26dc59b9c2dcf0b772c674a3b","tid":131753,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:30:10.000Z","msg":"良心警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}